OL,3,CFormer Senedd Member in palliative
OL,4,Ccare after a sudden sepsis diagnosis
OL,6,FA former Senedd Member is receiving
OL,7,Fpalliative care after a sudden sepsis
OL,8,Fdiagnosis.
OL,10,FCaroline Jones was a UKIP Assembly
OL,11,FMember from May 2016 and April 2021
OL,12,Ffor South Wales West and stood in last
OL,13,Fweek's election as an Independent
OL,14,Fcandidate.
OL,16,FPosting on Facebook, her husband Alun
OL,17,FWilliams wrote: "It is with heavy
OL,18,Fhearts that I must share that Caroline
OL,19,FJones is currently receiving
OL,20,Fpalliative care following a diagnosis
OL,21,Fof severe sepsis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
