PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778702756
OL,3,CFormer Senedd Member in palliative
OL,4,Ccare after a sudden sepsis diagnosis
OL,6,F"This has all happened very suddenly,
OL,7,Fand our family is trying to come to
OL,8,Fterms with everything while making
OL,9,Fsure Caroline is comfortable and
OL,10,Fsurrounded by love.
OL,12,F"We know that Caroline means so much
OL,13,Fto many people, and we wanted to keep
OL,14,Ffriends and loved ones informed.
OL,16,F"Your messages, thoughts, and prayers
OL,17,Fare deeply appreciated during this
OL,18,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
