OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778702756
OL,3,CFormer Senedd Member in palliative
OL,4,Ccare after a sudden sepsis diagnosis
OL,6,FMs Jones joined Reform UK in 2023 and
OL,7,Fstood as the party's candidate for
OL,8,FBridgend in the 2024 General Election.
OL,9,FShe quit the party in April this year
OL,10,Fand instead ran as stood as an
OL,11,FIndependent for Pen-y-bont Bro
OL,12,FMorgannwg.
OL,14,FHer husband wrote: "She cared so
OL,15,Fdeeply and passionately for people and
OL,16,Falways wanted to help others," adding:
OL,17,F"She will be truly and sadly missed.
OL,18,FMy whole world has come to an end. A
OL,19,Fgorgeous, vibrant and loving lady."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
