OL,3,CFormer Senedd Member in palliative
OL,4,Ccare after a sudden sepsis diagnosis
OL,6,FBridgend Councillor Owain Clatworthy
OL,7,Fshared a picture of him with Ms Jones
OL,8,Fon social media platform X, writing:
OL,9,F"Really saddened by the news about my
OL,10,Ffriend, campaign manager & former
OL,11,FMember of the Senedd Caroline Jones.
OL,13,F"My thoughts and prayers are with Alun
OL,14,Fand all of the family during this
OL,15,Fincredibly difficult time. Praying for
OL,16,Fcomfort, peace and strength for
OL,17,Feveryone around her."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
